<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 28 日，星期日 11:18:42 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Russia May Increase Grain Export to Egypt]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110654410" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1b/1110629166_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_ca9f611cc4342b5078ae28f57271fa74.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110629148" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/russia-may-increase-grain-export-to-egypt-1110654410.html?share-img=1110629148"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Alexander Kryazhev</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">小麦</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Wheat - Sputnik International, 1920, 28.05.2023" title="小麦" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1b/1110629166_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_ce513d0f3b689d20d8efbba77d8383d0.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1b/1110629166_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_5f89794ea65d76e9e401fd9f1fd389c7.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1b/1110629166_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_3f614b537d86437e8d6f423435a192ba.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1b/1110629166_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_ce513d0f3b689d20d8efbba77d8383d0.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Alexander Kryazhev</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：俄罗斯-埃及商业委员会主席周日对人造卫星表示，只要克服后勤挑战，俄罗斯就有“潜在的生产能力”来扩大对埃及的粮食出口。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “这是一个困难、复杂的问题。俄罗斯会增加粮食出口吗？答案是肯定的，因为俄罗斯的产量正在上升，”米哈伊尔·奥尔洛夫说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">埃及的粮食需求与该国人口的增长同步增长。奥尔洛夫表示，俄罗斯需要解决因西方对莫斯科实施制裁而产生的海运和其他后勤问题。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “但俄罗斯有一定程度的弹性，因此出口将继续，”奥尔洛夫补充道。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯和乌克兰于 2022 年夏季达成了一项由联合国和土耳其斡旋的协议，以促进<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230522/kremlin-on-grain-deal-position-of-western-countries-complicates-process-1110517064.html" target="_blank">乌克兰谷物</a>从黑海港口出口，并解除西方对俄罗斯谷物和化肥出口的限制。俄罗斯警告说，只要其出口能力仍然受到限制，它就可能不会将协议延长到 7 月 17 日的最后期限之后。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 11:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/russia-may-increase-grain-export-to-egypt-1110654410.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/russia-may-increase-grain-export-to-egypt-1110654410.html<category>经济</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>埃及</category><category>粮食出口</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[New Chinese-Made Passenger Plane C919 Makes First Commercial Flight - State Media]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110654111" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105195/55/1051955538_0:0:5184:3456_1440x900_80_0_1_013b1d8db56c3b3d371f8d23cb098f44.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1051955537" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/new-chinese-made-passenger-plane-c919-makes-first-commercial-flight---state-media-1110654111.html?share-img=1051955537"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / STR /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">中国第一架大型客机 C919（文件）</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="China's first big passenger plane C919 (File) - Sputnik International, 1920, 28.05.2023" title="中国第一架大客机C919（资料）" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105195/55/1051955538_0:270:5184:3186_1920x0_80_0_0_1ce764767667c173b9f23fe7ce77d61d.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105195/55/1051955538_0:270:5184:3186_640x0_80_0_0_f610c2b66323560b496eb1c18a09b2c5.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105195/55/1051955538_0:270:5184:3186_1280x0_80_0_0_fe13a1ae5a21d8b50b97b9c265d60b81.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105195/55/1051955538_0:270:5184:3186_1920x0_80_0_0_1ce764767667c173b9f23fe7ce77d61d.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©<a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">法新社 2023</a> / STR / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据北京（人造卫星）网报道：据中国电视台报道，中国干线客机 C919 的首次商业飞行于周日成功进行。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">中国东方航空公司官方应用程序称，该飞机于5月28日从上海虹桥国际机场乘坐MU9191航班飞往北京邵都国际机场，于当地时间10:32（格林威治标准时间02:32）起飞。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">飞机已经降落在北京。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2022 年 12 月 9 日，中国国有航空航天制造商中国商用飞机有限责任公司 (COMAC) 将<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20181229/china-third-prototype-completes-flight-c919-1071080462.html" target="_blank">首架 C919</a>交付给中国最大的航空公司之一中国东方航空公司。该机的注册号为B-919A，“B”代表中国民航飞机，“919”对应型号名称，“A”代表系列首架。其容量为 164 个座位：商务舱 8 个，经济舱 156 个。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> C919 型是中国第一架长途客机，座位数为 158 至 174 个，航程可达 5,500 公里（3,417 英里）。该项目由中国商飞于 2007 年启动，并在西方供应商的广泛参与下实施。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">中国商飞计划总共出售至少 2,000 架 C919 客机。 2018年，公司通报，当时28家中外客户采购<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20221109/chinas-comac-receives-over-300-new-orders-for-home-grown-c919-airliner-after-zhuhai-air-show-demo-1103948644.html" target="_blank">C919</a>的订单总数达到815架。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 10:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/new-chinese-made-passenger-plane-c919-makes-first-commercial-flight---state-media-1110654111.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/new-chinese-made-passenger-plane-c919-makes-first-commercial-flight---state-media-1110654111.html<category>亚洲</category><category>科学与技术</category><category>上海</category><category>C919</category><category>中国商用飞机有限责任公司 (COMAC)</category><category>中国</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Saudi Arabia 'in Talks' to Join BRICS Bank to Enhance 'Funding Options']]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110651647" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/17/1096603406_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_1e1606a48ad282b66536cdc922d37055.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1096603389" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/saudi-arabia-in-talks-to-join-brics-bank-to-enhance-funding-options-1110651647.html?share-img=1096603389"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Alexei Danichev</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">金砖国家</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="BRICS - Sputnik International, 1920, 28.05.2023" title="金砖国家" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/17/1096603406_0:160:3073:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_64f767e1c83a58c44342ab703000b01f.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/17/1096603406_0:160:3073:1888_640x0_80_0_0_98927ec5d7d2b13d7fae09637b016e1d.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/17/1096603406_0:160:3073:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_3385d507c764f90706ac7ac4efc64608.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/06/17/1096603406_0:160:3073:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_64f767e1c83a58c44342ab703000b01f.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Alexei Danichev</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">斯韦特兰娜·埃基缅科</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_svetlana_ekimenko/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:s.ekimenko@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">莫斯科认为金砖国家新开发银行 (NDB) 的主要目标之一是保护该集团成员国（巴西、俄罗斯、印度、中国和南非）免受“西方集体的非法制裁”，俄罗斯总理Mikhail Mishustin 最近访问中国参加一个商业论坛时强调了这一点。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国媒体报道援引<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230330/china-welcomes-dilma-rousseff-as-head-of-brics-bank-1108957625.html#:~:text=China%20Welcomes%20Dilma%20Rousseff%20as%20Head%20of%20BRICS%E2%80%99%20Bank" target="_blank">新开发银行的一份声明称，沙特阿拉伯正在就加入总部位于上海的新开发银行</a>（也称为“金砖国家银行”）进行谈判。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “在中东，我们非常重视沙特阿拉伯王国，目前正在与他们进行有条件的对话，”贷方的声明中写道。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110651647" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/saudi-arabia-in-talks-to-join-brics-bank-to-enhance-funding-options-1110651647.html?share-block=1110651785" data-title="“In the Middle East, we attach great importance to the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and are currently engaged in a qualified dialogue with them,” the statement by the lender read."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">它补充说，将该国添加为该银行的第九个成员将加强利雅得与金砖国家成员国的关系。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报告强调，希望世界上最大的石油出口国加入该银行，因为这将有助于加强其融资选择。新开发银行独立评估办公室主任 Ashwani Muthoo 将后者列为“<em>当前最重要的事情</em>”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “<em>我们正在努力调动资源</em>，”他说，并补充说，在即将召开的董事会会议上，新开发银行董事会打算研究替代货币，例如中国的人民币（也称为人民币）或南非兰特。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p> NDB 于 2014 年根据金砖国家巴西、俄罗斯、印度、中国和南非达成的协议成立，被视为西方领导的布雷顿森林机构（如世界银行、国际货币基金组织和一般金融机构）的替代选择关税和贸易协定——世界贸易组织的前身。 NDB 旨在通过提供贷款、担保和其他金融工具作为国家和私人项目的一部分，为<a href="https://sputniknews.com/20230215/brics-to-discuss-reforming-global-political-and-economic-architecture-south-africa-says-1107453992.html">金砖</a>国家以及其他新兴市场和发展中国家的项目调动资源。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2021 年，该银行接纳孟加拉国、埃及、阿联酋和乌拉圭为新成员。除乌拉圭外，所有这些国家均在交存加入书后正式成为成员。创始成员俄罗斯持有该银行约 19% 的股份。然而，在去年乌克兰危机期间，该银行不得不暂停在俄罗斯的交易，理由是“<em>不断出现的不确定性和限制</em>”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>但北约与俄罗斯在乌克兰的代理人战争带来的制裁和上述限制加速了一场戏剧性的全球调整，引发了关于美元替代品的新讨论，美元已成为西方胁迫其他国家屈服的工具。</strong>最近率领高调代表团出席俄中商业论坛的俄罗斯总理米哈伊尔·米舒斯京强调，新开发银行有助于保护金砖国家免受“来自西方集体的非法制裁”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">越来越多的因素表明，美元正在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/emerging-market-investors-dump-dollar-denominated-debt-as-currency-continues-global-decline-1110499206.html" target="_blank">失去其作为国际公认的主要价值储存手段的地位</a>。 <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230522/bolivia-advances-in-replacing-dollar-with-yuan-for-trade-with-china-1110523311.html" target="_blank">越来越多的国家</a>正在努力增加当地货币的使用。一个典型的例子是金砖国家（它们现在在整体经济实力方面已经超过七国集团）关于建立一种替代美元的共同货币的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230512/brics-to-discuss-common-currency-amid-de-dollarization--1110291379.html" target="_blank">讨论</a>。目前正准备加入新开发银行的沙特阿拉伯一直<a href="https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/saudi-arabia-open-trading-currencies-besides-us-dollar">表示对美元以外的货币交易持开放态度</a>，其中最引人注目的是人民币。这个盛产石油的王国的财政部长在一月份宣布了这一消息。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">近年来，北京一直在扩大与利雅得在经济、军事和成功的外交团队合作等方面的合作——最近中国促成的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230312/delusional-israeli-leaders-hit-out-at-each-other-after-iran-saudi-arabia-normalize-ties-1108301247.html" target="_blank">伊朗与沙特阿拉伯关系</a>的复苏就是证明。中国国家主席习近平去年访问了沙特阿拉伯，称赞两国关系进入“新时代”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，据报道，沙特阿拉伯一直在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20221018/saudi-arabia-shows-interest-in-joining-brics-south-african-president-says-1102017861.html#:~:text=Saudi%20Arabia%20Shows%20Interest%20in%20Joining%20BRICS%2C%20South%20African%20President%20Says">考虑加入金砖国家</a>。该集团联合了世界上最大的发展中经济体——巴西、俄罗斯、印度、中国和南非。最近一段时间，其他一些国家对加入金砖国家表现出浓厚的兴趣，金砖国家占世界人口的40%以上，占全球经济产出的近三分之一。在定于 8 月 22 日在南非约翰内斯堡举行的集团峰会之前，官员和分析人士一直在扩大金砖国家在此次活动中考虑<a href="https://sputniknews.com/20220712/brics-could-create-its-own-reserve-currency-russias-medvedev-says-1097230782.html" target="_blank">这种新形式货币</a>的可能性。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 10:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/saudi-arabia-in-talks-to-join-brics-bank-to-enhance-funding-options-1110651647.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/saudi-arabia-in-talks-to-join-brics-bank-to-enhance-funding-options-1110651647.html<category>世界</category><category>沙特阿拉伯</category><category>米哈伊尔·米舒斯汀</category><category>新开发银行 (NDB)</category><category>中国</category><category>金砖国家</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>利雅得</category><category>元</category></item></channel></rss>